<p>A series of mudslides triggered by days of heavy rain struck the western Rift Valley in Elgeyo-Marakwet County on Saturday, killing at least 21 people and leaving about 30 others missing, authorities said as search efforts were paused for the day for safety reasons . Aerial footage and initial assessments show large swathes of mud and flash flooding across the hilly Chesongoch area, which has isolated communities and complicated rescue access . Local and national teams say recovery and search operations are ongoing as officials begin damage assessments and relief coordination .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/YUW5FTB1KG7aPwRRk95P2RbZyJ9l2e-ToHviuUFtWjarWEOl1-_ivJ3tZYgP2vh88orKrVyNot1UhoFjP_K8TXep8ZjHfGAXyyGIkabq3QQ66DYwpHIe2Ve3zGrHTc2s_NnBu1mjjSDBbKIzklnCYbZbDHHNyPzoEWwoero_IR8kvkZ7z2BolPag58wKXkiK3HPhOhuwCSPL9lQ0UGAw9H39hEQ-Rw8dkv-yIyQ14aS7jCWjfp9f73TUJerTQKrkaaRDhKqg6Yf4' alt='Mud and destroyed homes after landslides in Elgeyo-Marakwet County, showing the scale of flooding and debris.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Widespread housing loss: Local reports and officials say more than 1,000 homes were destroyed by the mudslides in Chesongoch, escalating displacement and shelter needs .</li><li>Aerial assessment: Aerial footage released by media and authorities shows massive mudflows and flash floods stretching across broad areas, which helped identify the hardest-hit zones for prioritizing rescues .</li><li>Access problems: Heavy rains damaged the road network in Marakwet East, leaving key routes impassable and complicating the delivery of aid and movement of search teams .</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Kenya interior ministry: The ministry reported casualties and said search operations were suspended for the day because conditions were unsafe, while coordination with local teams continues. (<a href='https://www.dw.com/en/kenya-landslide-kills-at-least-21-after-heavy-rains/a-74587337'>DW</a>)</li><li>Elgeyo-Marakwet county officials: County authorities described widespread mudflows across hilly communities and are working with national agencies to assess damage and reach isolated residents. (<a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/11/2/landslides-in-kenyas-rift-valley-leave-21-dead-30-others-missing'>Al Jazeera</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/kenya-landslide-kills-at-least-21-after-heavy-rains/a-74587337'>Kenya: Landslide kills at least 21 after heavy rains</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/11/2/landslides-in-kenyas-rift-valley-leave-21-dead-30-others-missing'>Landslides in Kenya’s Rift Valley leave 21 dead, 30 others missing</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.firstpost.com/world/landslide-in-kenyas-rift-valley-leaves-21-dead-dozens-missing-13947077.html'>Landslide in Kenya’s Rift Valley leaves 21 dead, dozens missing</a> - firstpost.com</li><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/2025/11/02/at-least-21-dead-and-more-than-1000-homes-destroyed-as-landslide-hits-kenyas-rift-valley'>At least 21 dead and more than 1,000 homes destroyed as landslide hits Kenya&#x27;s Rift Valley</a> - euronews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/21-dead-over-30-missing-in-kenya-landslide-interior-minister-9559202#publisher=newsstand'>21 Dead, Over 30 Missing In Kenya Landslide: Interior Minister</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c20eeqn2qlyo'>Kenyan landslide kills 21 after heavy rainfall</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/several-killed-missing-in-landslip-kenya-rains-latest-update-november-2/article70231849.ece'>21 killed, 30 others missing in landslip in western Kenya</a> - thehindu.com</li><li><a href='https://apnews.com/article/kenya-landslides-elgeyo-marakwet-rift-valley-900f900b8463da42039bc046fcb66013'>A landslide triggered by heavy rain kills at least 21 people and leaves 30 others missing in Rift Valley Province, Kenya.</a> - apnews.com</li></u